(52, 40, 9, '80', '2019', '2019-01-05 07:16:41', 'Target jelas dengan measurement.\n\nNamun korelasi antara langkah dengan hasil yang diinginkan tidak di state dengan jelas.\n\nBagaimana dengan improvement internal untuk memastikan semua project/rencana on time. Harap rencanakan perbaikan internal juga dari segi: dokumentasi/filling, manajemen, dan reporting.'),
(53, 41, 9, '75', '2019', '2019-01-05 07:18:03', 'Improvement hanya bersifat external departement/pelanggan. Perlu ada improvement internal untuk meningkatkan:\n1. Kualitas kerja (hasil valid)\n2. Ketepatan kerja (deadline)\n3. Kompetensi tim (kemampuan hitung belum seimbang)\n4. Teamwork'),
(54, 9, 3, '80', '2019', '2019-02-23 06:36:13', 'the daily morning meeting between the forman and staff is good\r\ntraining to upgrade skill of workers need to be more intenif and target oriented\r\npreventive maintenance should be better\r\nMaintenance and service cards system is ongoing'),
(55, 10, 3, '75', '2019', '2019-02-23 06:39:53', 'the day to day operation and trouble shooting is quite good ,\nthe workers skill need to be upgraded\nMainteneance stii need to be improved ,but overall it is in fairly good level\n'),
(56, 11, 3, '80', '2019', '2019-02-23 06:44:20', 'Overall the action done toward work completion is satisfactoryly\r\nthe internal work coordination can be improved\r\nMaintenance and service record shoul be improved\r\nWorkers skill to some extents should have upgrade program'),
